  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward commits and scan (full_rotate) commits to maximize marker detection.",
    "On marker_seen, immediately commit to marker approach with move_to_marker until marker_close.",
    "On marker_close, stop to ensure safe task completion.",
    "Handle all uncontrollable events in every state to guarantee safe, deadlock-free operation.",
    "After obstacle detection, recover with a safe action (backward or rotate), then scan before resuming forward.",
    "Commit states enforce persistent actions and prevent oscillations.",
    "Never allow move_forward after obstacle_front without a recovery/scan step.",
    "Exploration is deprioritized when marker is visible; marker pursuit is always preferred.",
    "Scan states are inserted after forward or recovery to maintain awareness and avoid long straight runs."
  ]
